TITLE: Episode 82 - Lucid Nightmare Pirate (featuring AlexONE)
DESCRIPTION: This week, we are talking to the man behind "Wood Chipper Goes Brrr." A solid dude with a musical mind and an ethereal wit. Join us to get to know this SKA loving punk and just have a gnarly time talking about punk, rule 34, dragon/car relationships, absurdist Twitter accounts, and more.
